reviewText: The seller was quick on delivery and was 100% accurate on product. Thank You
Great movie if you like this genre.  Seen it many times and still makes me laugh.
Purchased this one only because Miles Teller was in it; however, even he couldn't make this movie any good. It was just dumb, not funny. I don't think I laughed once.

I truly enjoyed this slapstick nature of this film.  Reminded me, to a much lesser degree, of the antics experienced during my own college days.  The cast is great and the scenarios are insanely funny.  Great for an unforgettable night of laughs with friends...
Very funny movie. It's a shame that it didn't seem to reach a mainstream audience.
